  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Take and put them on the stretcher, sometime in two bodies together, depend on the size the bodies, opened the door of the oven.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody's pushing the stretcher in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody else holding with a kind of a piece of wire on, holding the bodies to take off the stretcher.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they start burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I said before, they were putting one woman on the center, just to get the flames to the dead bodies of the men.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was almost happening every week, 3,000 of Jewish people coming from different places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we-- when we was not 3,000-- the transport were not coming all the time-- they used to bring about 200, 300 from inside of the-- of the camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- kill-- they used to kill them not with the gas in the gas chamber, because the gas chamber was for 3,000, just to get it inside, like a piece of sardines.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the way-- the way those 6,000 people they were killed with asphyxia call them?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody from the [INAUDIBLE] was thrown in the-- this kind of a gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know why they call them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Zyklon B?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so they would kill them [INAUDIBLE] of the bunker downstairs, those 200 or 300 people with a-- with a German, with a shotgun, one by one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of us used to hold the prisoner from the ear and tell him-- and tell him, because they didn't know what was going on, and now they were going to kill.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Holding the ear like this, and the-- hiding [INAUDIBLE] of the-- of the German, just shoot him in the back of the head.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
